OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry throughout the day. There
OL,6,Fwill be a good deal of sunshine but
OL,7,Fsome patchy low cloud may come and go
OL,8,Falong eastern coasts. Warm across
OL,9,FOrkney. Fresh south or southeasterly
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,13,Fsome sunshine. Then the rest of the
OL,14,Fnight will remain dry with prolonged
OL,15,Fclear periods. Fresh southerly winds,
OL,16,Feasing later.
OL,17,
OL,18,CFriday:FMost of the day will be dry
OL,19,Fwith some hazy sunshine. High cloud
OL,20,Fthickening through the afternoon to
OL,21,Fbring the odd light shower by evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
