OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fover the weekend with the chance of a
OL,7,Ffew showers, but some dry weather too.
OL,8,FEarly rain on Monday followed by
OL,9,Fshowers, turning colder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
